<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4593933>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Zyzzogeton emmrichi sp. nov., male holotype. (A) Body, dorsal view. (B) Body, lateral view. (C) Anterior region of body (showing head and prothorax in greater detail), lateral view. (D) Pygofer and anal tube, lateral view. (E) Valve and subgenital plates, ventral view. (F) Connective and style, dorsal view. (G) Aedeagus, lateral view. (H) Apical portion of aedeagus, dorsal view. LAT: lobed anal tube (segment X), OSL: outer style lobe, VLV: valve. (Scale bars: (A), (B), 5 mm; (C–G), 1 mm; (H), 0.5 mm.)" ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4593933/files/figure.png" .

